{
  "title": "Purely Plantbased Tunisian Lentil Tagine",
  "description": "A flavorful and nutritious Tunisian stew made with lentils, sultanas, and aromatic spices, perfect for a solo dinner, this dish is earthy, molten, and plant-based-friendly",
  "cuisine": "Tunisian",
